


   LORD OF ALCANDRIA - Chapter III

   created by Edgardo Federico Rutenberg  


   e-mail me at:  edi@dd.com.ar
                  or  masterkey@uole.com
         

   The Game has been tested on: Amiga 1200 standard HD
                                Amiga 1200 030/40mhz HD 16mb ram

   Lord of Alcandria is designed to work on any Amiga with Hard Disk,
   and 2meg chip, even on an A500 machine.



   Installing Lord of Alcandria: Simply drag the directory Lord_of_Alcandria
                                 into the destination path.             


   The game controls: Left mouse - walk around and select
                      Right mouse - unite the action on the main screen
                      F1 to F10 load previously saved games
                      SHIFT+F1 to F10 save game
                      Q quits the game 
                      Ctrl + C crack the game
                      C chip memory available
                      M total memory available



